Package: lcsm
Type: Package
Title: Specifying, analysing, and visualising latent change score models
Date: 2019-05-23
Version: 0.0.3.9001
Authors@R: c(
  person("Milan", "Wiedemann", email = "milan.wiedemann@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1991-282X"))
  )
Description: Helper functions to define and analyse univariate and bivariate latent change score (LCS) models using the R package lavaan.
  The package offers functions to select cases to be used for the analyses based on the number of available data points. 
  Plotting functions help to visualise longitudunal data (ggplot2) as well as simplified path models (semPlot).
  The lavaan syntax that gets created by the package can be extracted for inspection and further manual specifications.
  Parameters and fit statistics can also be extracted (broom).
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
